				<p>The obligations and responsibilities set out in this Privacy Policy are applicable to Fastmetrics and its personnel and will be made available on Fastmetrics’ website (<a href="https://www.Fastmetrics.com/privacy-policy">www.Fastmetrics.com/privacy-policy</a>).&nbsp; The obligations and responsibilities set out in the Privacy Policy are in addition to any other applicable policies or agreements entered into with Fastmetrics&nbsp; and any applicable laws and/or regulations.</p>
				<h2>General Statement</h2>
				<p>Fastmetrics is dedicated to the use of <a href="https://www.fastmetrics.com/blog/phone-systems/what-is-voip-how-does-it-work/">Voice over Internet Protocol (VoIP)</a> and related technologies to improve the telecommunications industry and the lives of individuals throughout the world.</p>
				<p>Fastmetrics’ goal is to deliver carrier-grade communications services to all its Clients, at a reasonable price and to make available all the benefits that VoIP offers as broadly as possible. In order to achieve this goal, a Privacy Policy is necessary.</p>
				<h2>Scope</h2>
				<p>At Fastmetrics, privacy matters.&nbsp; Fastmetrics respects the privacy of its Clients and other individuals with whom Fastmetrics has business interactions</p>
